title: Simon white LIVE 30-03-08 Paradiso Main Hall
description:
Simone White LIVE in concert 30/3/08 at the Paradiso Main Hall.

Torrent contains the FLV file of the entire concert and my attempts to to convert them to AVI files. Concert 1 is with unchanged audio. Concert 2 is with mp3 audio. Both conversions may suffer from synch problems if you try to play them on your DVD players.

Anyway sound quality is great, picture quality is ok. [400x300]
